{"tid":1776202,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「厲害了我的國」，基因改造出「人腦猴子」","createTime":"2019-12-09T11:06:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T12:22:35.000Z","uid":184099,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"cd887cb5e347d203a3a50ea43fa5587ca676225b","tid":1776202,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:06:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://theme.udn.com/theme/story/6775/4214063\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheme.udn.com%2Ftheme%2Fstory%2F6775%2F4214063&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2Fwmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=84065bdd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theme.udn.com/theme/story/6775/4214063</a><br />\n<br />\n只講重點，全文自己入去睇。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">首先，</span></strong><br />\n該團隊處理了4000多個胚胎，所有胚胎都植入了母豬，最終只有10隻豬仔出生。豬仔的外觀基本保持不變，但科學家能觀察到猴細胞，這些猴細胞經過基因編輯以發出螢光，從而易於觀察。在10隻豬仔中，實際上只有兩隻是混合體。兩隻豬仔都在出生後一周內死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">這項研究的目的是努力提高在豬身上培育器官的能力，研究目標是希望未來不需從人身上移植器官，而能使用豬身上培育即用型人體器官。</span></strong>但實驗成果曝光後，惹來多國科學家批評，指該研究在道德倫理上令人震驚。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">然後，</span></strong><br />\n今年4月，大陸科學家培育出11隻攜有人類基因的恒河猴，這些猴子的大腦發育表現出接近人類大腦發育的特徵，只存活了5隻。再次在國際間引發倫理爭議。<br />\n<br />\n綜合美國之音中文網等報導，中國科學院昆明動物研究所宣布，該所與多個研究團隊合作，首次建構了攜帶人類MCPH1基因複製的基因改造恒河猴模型，獲得11隻基因改造猴。中科院宣稱，相對於野生猴，基因改造猴工作記憶能力「明顯提高」，說明大腦發育延緩可能提升了基因改造猴的智力。<br />\n<br />\n中科院的聲明說，這項研究成果「顯示了轉基因（基因改造）猴模型對研究人類起源以及人類特有腦疾病（如老年癡呆等）的重要價值」。"},{"pid":"6092b1cf145c4a1d583452225b10f135f31c93c8","tid":1776202,"uid":184099,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:09:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望快d研究出人體器官。<br />\n<br />\n到時2047香港人唔洗好似新疆咁，<br />\n比人劏開黎拎器官。<br />\n<br />\n加油，厲害的祖國<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"992187b5a16fffc755f66bdd8c7e7b5a93e82b63","tid":1776202,"uid":286155,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:10:37.000Z","msg":"爭霸戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd46d3ea199df69dbd8a320daf1f1f86268ce14d","tid":1776202,"uid":220601,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:12:39.000Z","msg":"洗撚研究，已經有13億隻啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37a92995856493577e49eade0dc6619b44b28e74","tid":1776202,"uid":76744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:13:55.000Z","msg":"Apes shall never kill apes."},{"pid":"f90e82456acd22a45a8d2123652fe116cbdec00c","tid":1776202,"uid":57211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:15:56.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},{"pid":"66ca13532df898656dd6ea8fd655c42faf3c2fa5","tid":1776202,"uid":192776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:18:28.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e942d37abe0bcb8d941e5d8d4e0916585af65c48","tid":1776202,"uid":31637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:18:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/e71/85b/e7185b28d26c268f0f4298587315d5e19a581561_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2Fe71%2F85b%2Fe7185b28d26c268f0f4298587315d5e19a581561_n.jpg&h=6b3623cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"09fb8ca1242dce3a8a8600ce68921228bafc0e41","tid":1776202,"uid":45120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:19:05.000Z","msg":"大陸好大機會會係電影入面唔小心俾改造生物走左出黎既國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"617d45bd5ad6ad3fa5cc293047d6a7b2c39be525","tid":1776202,"uid":41998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:19:44.000Z","msg":"遲早出事<i